attaining his or her fitness goals, whatever the level of athletic
ability, said Wiliam Squires, professor of health fitness and
nutrition at Texas Lutheran College and chairman of the task force
that developed FYT. It also teaches students about the importance
of maintaining physical activity throughout life.
